testScript.details:
Given that the customer is on the login screen;

And want to creat account by clicking on "Create account";

When the user finishes filling in the required fields (on the account creation screen), the user clicks on the “Confirm” button;

Then your account will be created and the message “Account created successfully” should be displayed.

Given that the customer is on the login screen;

When adding an unregistered username;

And add an 8-digit password in the password field;

When you press the “Login” button;

Then the message “Invalid password and/or E-mail” should appear to the user.

Given that the customer is on the login screen;

And is not registered in the system;

When customer click on the “Reset password” button, a text box appears for him to enter the e-mail;

Then the message “Invalid password and/or E-mail” should appear to the user.

Given that the customer is on the login screen;

And is not registered in the system;

When customer click on the “Forgot password” button, a text box appears for him to enter the e-mail;

Then the message “Invalid password and/or E-mail” should appear to the user.
